         <li class="touchcarousel-item"><img width="683" height="460" src="http://www.drew.edu/undergraduate/wp-content/uploads/sites/106/fichtman3.jpg" class="attachment-thepeople wp-post-image" alt="fichtman"> <h2 class="type">Full-Impact Students</h2> <h2 class="name">Taylor Fichtman</h2> <p>I now know that I want my future profession to be multilingual. I studied abroad twice in Spain, and it’s helped me respect other societies’ ways.</p> </li> 
