         <li class="touchcarousel-item"><img width="683" height="460" src="http://www.drew.edu/undergraduate/wp-content/uploads/sites/106/herrara1.jpg" class="attachment-thepeople wp-post-image" alt="herrara"> <h2 class="type">Passionate Faculty</h2> <h2 class="name">Raúl Rosales Herrera</h2> <h2>Associate professor</h2> <p>In addition to autobiography and self-representation, my research examines popular culture and melodramatic modalities in the Spanish-speaking world. I am also a proud Drew alumnus.</p> <p><strong>Ph.D., Columbia University</strong></p> </li> 
