    <section id="thecourses" class="container thecourses"> 
     <h2>My Favorite Course</h2> 
     <blockquote>
      <p>“I helped teach English to day laborers at the Neighborhood House in Morristown, N.J. It was amazing. For a year I was able to practice my Spanish skills outside the class setting.”</p>
